ious cultures, and their performances can only be understood in those contexts.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aDemoniac possessionzEuropexHistory. 0aExorcismzEuropexHistory. 7aRELIGION / Christianity / History.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030019538540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300195385423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300195385/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles